text: Elias Van Breussegem (born 10 April 1992) is a Belgian cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Continental team . ==Major results== ;2014 : 1st 20px Time trial, National Under-23 Road Championships ;2015 : 4th Grote Prijs Stad Zottegem ;2016 : 1st Omloop Het Nieuwsblad U23 : 7th Overall Le Triptyque des Monts et Châteaux : 9th Duo Normand (with Christophe Prémont) ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
